help:reset;help:reset boundary;help:reset colors;help:reset rotation;help:reset rot
                          reset boundary

                Removes the figure except vertices.
     If convexhull is set, figure is immediately recalculated.


                          reset colors

            Sets all the colors to their default values.
It is applied to background, facecolor, selvertcolor, spacecolor*.


                          reset rot[ation]

              Rotates figure to its default rotation.
